{"tid":1495543,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"工程學徒約(滿師紙)一問","createTime":"2019-08-22T06:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T11:44:19.000Z","uid":78576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d23de87cefe16eadb8dc4590481d7a4c76bb1bbb","tid":1495543,"uid":78576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T06:03:18.000Z","msg":"想問問各位巴打,師兄<br />\n<br />\n我之前簽左學徒約  一直都半工讀個HD  係呢行已經做左差唔多4年<br />\n咁今年其實已經讀完個HD     但係個學徒約  重有一年半<br />\n本身做緊AE  但最近因為公司同工作問題  今個月祼辭左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問張學徒滿師紙重唔重要?  <br />\n因為我諗緊直接搵其他工好  定係唔理份學徒約  因為公司已經解約  or  <br />\n搵間公司補簽張學徒約 攞滿師紙 但要玩一年半,人工 可能好低同埋職位未必搵到AE 可能唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望各位比d 意見  thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82bdba4f0598c9f2cfb999c1cba3dab99103a87","tid":1495543,"uid":36994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T06:16:46.000Z","msg":"洗撚咩 最緊要係張工作證明"},{"pid":"4c1bf025a5da59bc4a8b7142e62e9ba6a4b69163","tid":1495543,"uid":78576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:11:34.000Z","msg":"工作證明  有搵舊公司大佬寫比我<br />\n咁張滿師紙 其實冇用?"},{"pid":"ca51ae1b4fc0fdebecb16da368310f790ad74fa8","tid":1495543,"uid":70505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:23:18.000Z","msg":"你拉工個陣問下一間肯唔肯補比你囉"},{"pid":"7b54321a51d930eb1f344da0c5b7b9bbbb8d6355","tid":1495543,"uid":147534,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:27:09.000Z","msg":"有HD仲要張爛鬼學徒cert托柒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349f202b83967e14751bb76ca41daef135114bef","tid":1495543,"uid":28244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:33:58.000Z","msg":"滿師紙還滿師紙 HD還HD 兩樣野 重要"},{"pid":"4fb4953da2263214d9fe9941e61ba560c1